le certification - Care Certificate duration - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Transferable certification - Care Certificate duration - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-32_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-33_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-35_">Once successfully completed, the Care Certificate is transferable from one workplace to another and does not expire. This means that once you obtain it, it will remain valid throughout your career. You won't need to renew or retake the assessment unless there are significant changes in legislation and policies or if you no longer possess the competencies necessary for the Care Certificate.<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-36_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-38_">Standards requiring refresher training </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Standards_requiring_refresher_training_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693487441" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Standards_requiring_refresher_training_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693487441 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Standards_requiring_refresher_training_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1693487441 320w" width="2000" height="1333" alt="Standards requiring refresher training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Standards requiring refresher training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-39_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-40_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-42_">There are, however, some standards within the Care Certificate that require refresher training. Topics such as basic life support, infection prevention and control, and safeguarding may need to be refreshed every 1 to 3 years. These timeframe